<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="infer-vt">infer <strong><em>vt</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /ɪn'fɜː(r)/    美 /ɪn'fɜːr/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>推断：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>I <strong>inferred</strong> the fact <strong>from</strong> the news.
我从这则消息中推断出这个事实。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>I <strong>inferred from</strong> his attitude that he didn't like her.
我从他的态度推断出他不喜欢她。</p></div>

<h2 id="_2">派生词汇</h2>
<p>inference  n   </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p><strong>make inferences</strong>
推理；推断</p></div></div>